    "VILENS [148] utilizes measurements from LiDAR, IMU, cameras, and leg contact information derived from a joint kinematics model.",
    "This inte-123 grated sensor fusion empowers the system to attain accurate odometry, even in demanding environments.Integrating multiple sensors for odometry presents practical solutions for addressing diverse environmental conditions.",
    "However, this approach comes with computational demands and introduces specific issues associated with each sensor.",
    "While sensor fusion can compensate for the limitations of individual sensors, the fusion process itself requires considerable effort.",
    "These limitations will be scrutinized further in Sect. 7.5."
